main event: A witness observed a light in the sky that was not a star or planet. The object was initially stationary, then moved rapidly away.
interesting points: The object appeared larger than a star and brighter.
The witness reported the sighting to the Air Force and was questioned by an officer.
The object was observed for about 30 seconds.
No photographs were taken of the object.
The witness described the object as a light that was not a star or planet.
sighted object: a light in the sky that was not a star or planet
